    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Distinctive pressed glass of various colors produced by the Boston Sandwich Glass Company. For double-wall glass objects with inner decoration of engraved gold leaf, use "gold glass (visual works)," having the UF "sandwich gold glass (visual works)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000021271/Newman, Illustrated Dictionary of Glass (1977)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Se refiere a los objetos de vidrio de doble pared con decoración interior de hojas de oro grabadas; también es un nombre general para el vidrio prensado, llamado así por la gran cantidad de vidrio prensado que produjo la Boston Sandwich Glass Company.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Te onderscheiden persglas met diverse kleuren dat werd geproduceerd door de Boston Sandwich Glass Company. Voor dubbelwandig glaswerk dat van binnen is versierd met gegraveerd goudblad, gebruik 'goldglass (beeldende werken)of het synoniem 'sandwich goldglass'.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>雙壁玻璃製品，內部飾有金箔雕刻。亦為壓製玻璃的通稱，因為大量的壓製玻璃出產於波士頓膠合玻璃公司（Boston Sandwich Glass Company）。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
